%99" title="อมรรตยะ เสน — thaï" lang="th" hreflang="th" class="interlanguage-link-target">ไทย</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-tl"><a href="https://tl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amartya_Sen" title="Amartya Sen — tagalog" lang="tl" hreflang="tl" class="interlanguage-link-target">Tagalog</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-tr"><a href="https://tr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amartya_Sen" title="Amartya Sen — turc" lang="tr" hreflang="tr" class="interlanguage-link-target">Türkçe</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-tt"><a href="https://tt.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%90%D0%BC%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%82%D1%8C%D1%8F_%D0%A1%D0%B5%D0%BD" title="Амартья Сен — tatar" lang="tt" hreflang="tt" class="interlanguage-link-target">Татарча/tatarça</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-uk"><a href="https://uk.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%90%D0%BC%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%82%D1%96%D1%8F_%D0%A1%D0%B5%D0%BD" title="Амартія Сен — ukrainien" lang="uk" hreflang="uk" class="interlanguage-link-target">Українська</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ur"><a href="https://ur.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D8%A7%D9%85%D8%B1%D8%AA%DB%8C%DB%81_%D8%B3%DB%8C%D9%86" title="امرتیہ سین — ourdou" lang="ur" hreflang="ur" class="interlanguage-link-target">اردو</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-uz"><a href="https://uz.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amartya_Sen" title="Amartya Sen — ouzbek" lang="uz" hreflang="uz" class="interlanguage-link-target">Oʻzbekcha/ўзбекча</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-vi"><a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amartya_Sen" title="Amartya Sen — vietnamien" lang="vi" hreflang="vi" class="interlanguage-link-target">Tiếng Việt</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-wuu"><a href="https://wuu.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%98%BF%E9%A9%AC%E8%92%82%E4%BA%9A%C2%B7%E5%BA%93%E9%A9%AC%E5%B0%94%C2%B7%E6%A3%AE" title="阿马蒂亚·库马尔·森 — wu" lang="wuu" hreflang="wuu" class="interlanguage-link-target">吴语</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-yo"><a href="https://yo.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amartya_Sen" title="Amartya Sen — yoruba" lang="yo" hreflang="yo" class="interlanguage-link-target">Yorùbá</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-zh"><a href="https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%98%BF%E9%A9%AC%E8%92%82%E4%BA%9A%C2%B7%E5%BA%93%E9%A9%AC%E5%B0%94%C2%B7%E6%A3%AE" title="阿马蒂亚·库马尔·森 — chinois" lang="zh" hreflang="zh" class="interlanguage-link-target">中文</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-zh-yue"><a href="https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%98%BF%E7%91%AA%E8%92%82%E4%BA%9E%E6%A3%AE" title="阿瑪蒂亞森 — Cantonese" lang="yue" hreflang="yue" class="interlanguage-link-target">粵語</a></li></ul>
