<th class="navbox-group" style="">1981-2000</th>
<td class="navbox-list" style=""><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r151529978"/><span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Vinoba_Bhave" title="Vinoba Bhave">Vinoba Bhave</a> (1983)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Khan_Abdul_Ghaffar_Khan" title="Khan Abdul Ghaffar Khan">Khan Abdul Ghaffar Khan</a> (1987)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/M._G._Ramachandran" title="M. G. Ramachandran">M. G. Ramachandran</a> (1988)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Bhimrao_Ramji_Ambedkar" title="Bhimrao Ramji Ambedkar">Bhimrao Ramji Ambedkar</a> et <a href="/wiki/Nelson_Mandela" title="Nelson Mandela">Nelson Mandela</a> (1990)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Rajiv_Gandhi" title="Rajiv Gandhi">Rajiv Gandhi</a>, <a href="/wiki/Vallabhbhai_Patel" title="Vallabhbhai Patel">Vallabhbhai Patel</a> et <a href="/wiki/Morarji_Desai" title="Morarji Desai">Morarji Desai</a> (1991)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Abul_Kalam_Azad" title="Abul Kalam Azad">Abul Kalam Azad</a>, <a href="/wiki/Jehangir_Ratanji_Dadabhai_Tata" title="Jehangir Ratanji Dadabhai Tata">Jehangir Ratanji Dadabhai Tata</a> et <a href="/wiki/Satyajit_Ray" title="Satyajit Ray">Satyajit Ray</a> (1992)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Gulzarilal_Nanda" title="Gulzarilal Nanda">Gulzarilal Nanda</a>, <a href="/wiki/Aruna_Asaf_Ali" title="Aruna Asaf Ali">Aruna Asaf Ali</a> et <a href="/wiki/Avul_Pakir_Jainulabdeen_Abdul_Kalam" title="Avul Pakir Jainulabdeen Abdul Kalam">Abdul Kalam</a> (1997)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/M._S._Subbulakshmi" title="M. S. Subbulakshmi">M. S. Subbulakshmi</a>  et <a href="/w/index.php?title=Chidambaram_Subramaniam&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink